data.description: Lovely 2 bedroom/2 bath lake front patio home located in a highly desired lake community. This treasure features a spacious great room with vaulted ceilings,  fireplace, open kitchen with eating area that open to cozy courtyard. Kitchen includes Refrigerator & cabinets with under mount lighting. Pantry area has washer/dryer & shelving.  Other features are a lovely Arizona room &  2 recently remodeled bathrooms. Delight your day with a fabulous deck overlooking a relaxing lake. This property is a one owner home that has been loved and maintained. Enjoy entertaining from your own back patio with a full lake view, perfect for a BBQ & more. Priced lower due to home needing interior paint. Community does feature a community club house.
